<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of this Regulation, notwithstanding Regulation (EC) No 2799/98: </inglise>
<eesti> Olenemata m&auml;&auml;rusest (E&Uuml;) nr 2799/98 kasutatakse k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses j&auml;rgmisi m&otilde;isteid: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) 'appreciable revaluation' means a reduction in the conversion rate applicable on 1 January 1999 which is greater in absolute value than the differencies between that rate and the lowest levels of the conversion rates applicable: </inglise>
<eesti> a) m&auml;rgatav revalveerimine - 1. jaanuaril 1999 kohaldatava &uuml;mberarvestuskursi langus, mille absoluutne v&auml;&auml;rtus on suurem kui nimetatud kursi ja kohaldatavate &uuml;mberarvestuskursside madalaima taseme vahe: </eesti>
<inglise> - over the last 12 months, and </inglise>
<eesti> - viimase 12 kuu jooksul, </eesti>
<inglise> - at any time more than 12 months but not more than 24 months previously, and </inglise>
<eesti> - &uuml;ksk&otilde;ik mis ajal, millest on m&ouml;&ouml;das 12-24 kuud, ja </eesti>
<inglise> - at any time more than 24 months but not more than 36 months previously. </inglise>
<eesti> - &uuml;ksk&otilde;ik mis ajal, millest on m&ouml;&ouml;das 24-36 kuud. </eesti>
<inglise> Only two thirds and one third respectively of the differences covered by the second and third indents shall be taken into account; </inglise>
<eesti> Teise taande puhul v&otilde;etakse nimetatud vahet arvesse ainult kahe kolmandiku ja kolmanda taande puhul &uuml;he kolmandiku ulatuses. </eesti>
<inglise> (b) 'appreciable part' means the difference between, on the one hand, the threshold between appreciable and non-appreciable revaluations and, on the other hand, the conversion rate for the euro into national currency units or the exchange rate for the euro into national currency on 1 January 1999. </inglise>
<eesti> b) m&auml;rgatava revalveerimise protsendim&auml;&auml;r - vahe m&auml;rgatava ja m&auml;rkamatu revalveerimise vahelise k&uuml;nnise ja 1. jaanuaril 1999 kehtiva euro omav&auml;&auml;ringutesse arvestamise kursi v&otilde;i omav&auml;&auml;ringute eurodeks vahetamise kursi vahel. </eesti>
<inglise> This difference is expressed as a percentage of the said threshold. </inglise>
